{"TopicId":148618,"ForumId":39,"TopicTitle":"Stock Pendulum Clock","CreatedByName":"Aphobius","CreatedById":79391,"CreatedDateTime":"2016-09-25T09:53:28Z","PageNum":1,"Articles":[{"CreatedByName":"Aphobius","CreatedById":79391,"CreatedDateTime":"2016-09-25T09:53:28Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nThis is a pendulum clock I\u0027ve made, it shows the seconds, minutes and hours. Everything is stock, done on a fresh install. I\u0027ve decided to make it after \u003Ca contenteditable=\u0022false\u0022 data-ipshover=\u0022\u0022 data-ipshover-target=\u0022https://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/index.php?/profile/97503-luizopiloto/\u0026amp;do=hovercard\u0022 data-mentionid=\u002297503\u0022 href=\u0022https://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/index.php?/profile/97503-luizopiloto/\u0022 rel=\u0022\u0022\u003E@luizopiloto\u003C/a\u003E showed me his \u003Ca href=\u0022https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=g19JNn3c1M4\u0022 rel=\u0022external nofollow\u0022\u003EVIDEO\u003C/a\u003E and suggested to me to make a clock.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nSo I\u0027ve added an hour hand since the previous video. Everything seems to work pretty well, but it\u0027s just not calibrated properly (it gained around 8 minutes in 2.5 hours), it can be calibrated and I could do it, but it\u0027s not really useful and it takes a very long time, because the game is running in slow motion and it takes a long time to load, every time I \u0022launch\u0022 the clock.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsEmbeddedVideo\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv\u003E\n\u003Ciframe allowfullscreen=\u0022true\u0022 frameborder=\u00220\u0022 height=\u0022270\u0022 src=\u0022https://www.youtube.com/embed/LVTVRuCC0VE?feature=oembed\u0022 width=\u0022480\u0022\u003E\u003C/iframe\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nAlso, if you want to see better how it\u0027s working, I\u0027ve made this video:\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n***WARNING***EXTREMELY BAD ENGLISH, ANNOYING VOICE AND TV IN BACKGROUND***WARNING***\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Ca href=\u0022https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=JgCQRGQ6iq8\u0022 rel=\u0022external nofollow\u0022\u003EExplanation video (I start the clock at 10:40)\u003C/a\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n***WARNING***EXTREMELY BAD ENGLISH, ANNOYING VOICE AND TV IN BACKGROUND***WARNING***\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nOLD POST:\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nI\u0027ve made a pendulum clock. It\u0027s showing the seconds and the minutes (you can compare them with the MET from the top left of the screen). In the 5 hours shown in the video (the video is speed up to 60x), it remained only around 35 seconds behind the real time (the longest calibration run was 15 minutes, so probably I could fix this). It has 759 parts.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nIf it gets boring skip to 4:30 for some nice shadows.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Ca href=\u0022https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=G2ugmoMK7oY\u0022 rel=\u0022external nofollow\u0022\u003Ehttps://www.youtube.com/watch?v=G2ugmoMK7oY\u003C/a\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nAnd a picture showing what its components are. The \u0022Spring\u0022 from the picture is actually a reaction wheel and by having the roll trim set to maximum (you can see it in the video), it spins by itself.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Cimg alt=\u0022beJyM67.jpg\u0022 class=\u0022ipsImage\u0022 height=\u0022655\u0022 src=\u0022http://i.imgur.com/beJyM67.jpg\u0022 width=\u00221000\u0022\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"luizopiloto","CreatedById":97503,"CreatedDateTime":"2016-09-25T21:21:34Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nKerbal Swatch\u00AE Program... \u003Cimg alt=\u0022:P\u0022 data-emoticon=\u0022\u0022 src=\u0022//kerbal-forum-uploads.s3.us-west-2.amazonaws.com/emoticons/default_k_tongue.gif\u0022 title=\u0022:P\u0022\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cspan class=\u0022ipsType_reset ipsType_medium ipsType_light\u0022 data-excludequote=\u0022\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cstrong\u003EEdited \u003Ctime datetime=\u00222016-09-25T21:22:05Z\u0022 title=\u002209/25/2016 09:22  PM\u0022 data-short=\u00227 yr\u0022\u003ESeptember 25, 2016\u003C/time\u003E by luizopiloto\u003C/strong\u003E\n\u003C/span\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Ultimate Steve","CreatedById":161505,"CreatedDateTime":"2016-09-25T21:37:13Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nHow is it possible to build such intricate contrpations in KSP? First the Rubik\u0027s cube, and now this! Hats off to you!\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"swjr-swis","CreatedById":152460,"CreatedDateTime":"2016-09-25T22:05:39Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00222774115\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022148618\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221474839433\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022161505\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022Ultimate Steve\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n20 minutes ago, Ultimate Steve said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nHow is it possible to build such intricate contrpations in KSP?\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nProbably because we stubbornly keep looking at parts and game mechanics in completely unintended ways, and then KSP doesn\u0027t stop us at just thinking \u0027what if...\u0027 but let\u0027s us try it. \u003Cimg alt=\u0022:D\u0022 data-emoticon=\u0022\u0022 src=\u0022//kerbal-forum-uploads.s3.us-west-2.amazonaws.com/emoticons/default_k_cheesy.gif\u0022 title=\u0022:D\u0022\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00222773352\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022148618\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221474797208\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u002279391\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022Aphobius\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n12 hours ago, Aphobius said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nI\u0027ve made a pendulum clock.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nI have a friend that makes a living revising and repairing antique and precision clockworks. I have this feeling I\u0027m gonna have to buy him KSP and beg you for the craft file the moment I show him your video. Awesome work.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Aphobius","CreatedById":79391,"CreatedDateTime":"2016-09-25T22:13:36Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nThank you for the nice words.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nYou motivate me to try to add an hour hand to it. I\u0027ll come back with a video if I succeed.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"katateochi","CreatedById":35181,"CreatedDateTime":"2016-09-25T22:26:31Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\nQuote\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nsurprise is no longer adequate and he is forced to resort to astonishment\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nThat quote about\u00A0Arthur Dent applies to me here. That is astonishing! Great job.\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00222774152\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022148618\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221474841616\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u002279391\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022Aphobius\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n11 minutes ago, Aphobius said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nI\u0027ll come back with a video if I succeed.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nI\u0027d like to see it running at real time and get a view of the workings.\u00A0\u003Cbr\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Aphobius","CreatedById":79391,"CreatedDateTime":"2016-09-26T18:50:06Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nI\u0027ve modified the first post, added a video with a new version of the clock, that has three hands and also added an \u0022explanation\u0022 video, but please take the ... disclaimer very seriously before you start it.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Kerbart","CreatedById":78303,"CreatedDateTime":"2016-09-26T19:04:32Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nThe video is, from 1:42 to 2:45, exceptionally riveting!\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nAll aside, impressive work!! I wouldn\u0027t mind if the video would be showing various parts of the inner workings of this clock though. Even in realtime/slow motion!\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Aphobius","CreatedById":79391,"CreatedDateTime":"2016-09-26T19:07:14Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nCheck the link under the first video, I show it in real time and I explain how it\u0027s working.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Andiron","CreatedById":141782,"CreatedDateTime":"2016-09-27T12:25:04Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nThis creation is epic. Great work \u003Ca contenteditable=\u0022false\u0022 data-ipshover=\u0022\u0022 data-ipshover-target=\u0022https://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/index.php?/profile/79391-aphobius/\u0026amp;do=hovercard\u0022 data-mentionid=\u002279391\u0022 href=\u0022https://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/index.php?/profile/79391-aphobius/\u0022 rel=\u0022\u0022\u003E@Aphobius\u003C/a\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Aphobius","CreatedById":79391,"CreatedDateTime":"2016-09-27T18:36:23Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00222776264\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022148618\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221474979104\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022141782\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022Andiron\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n6 hours ago, Andiron said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nThis creation is epic. Great work \u003Ca contenteditable=\u0022false\u0022 data-ipshover=\u0022\u0022 data-ipshover-target=\u0022https://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/index.php?/profile/79391-aphobius/\u0026amp;do=hovercard\u0022 data-mentionid=\u002279391\u0022 href=\u0022https://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/index.php?/profile/79391-aphobius/\u0022 rel=\u0022\u0022\u003E@Aphobius\u003C/a\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nThank you. \u003Cimg alt=\u0022:)\u0022 data-emoticon=\u0022\u0022 src=\u0022//kerbal-forum-uploads.s3.us-west-2.amazonaws.com/emoticons/default_k_smiley.gif\u0022 title=\u0022:)\u0022\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"TheDestroyer111","CreatedById":160216,"CreatedDateTime":"2016-09-27T19:40:20Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00222773352\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022148618\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221474797208\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u002279391\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022Aphobius\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\nOn 9/25/2016 at 11:53 AM, Aphobius said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nThis is a pendulum clock I\u0027ve made, it shows the seconds, minutes and hours. Everything is stock, done on a fresh install. I\u0027ve decided to make it after \u003Ca contenteditable=\u0022false\u0022 data-ipshover=\u0022\u0022 data-ipshover-target=\u0022https://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/index.php?/profile/97503-luizopiloto/\u0026amp;do=hovercard\u0022 data-mentionid=\u002297503\u0022 href=\u0022https://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/index.php?/profile/97503-luizopiloto/\u0022 rel=\u0022\u0022\u003E@luizopiloto\u003C/a\u003E showed me his \u003Ca href=\u0022https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=g19JNn3c1M4\u0022 rel=\u0022external nofollow\u0022\u003EVIDEO\u003C/a\u003E and suggested to me to make a clock.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nAbsolutely speechless.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nAFTER cooling down a bit, here\u0027s my reaction to this device:\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Cimg alt=\u0022XpV3FaY.png\u0022 class=\u0022ipsImage\u0022 height=\u0022666\u0022 src=\u0022http://i.imgur.com/XpV3FaY.png\u0022 width=\u00221000\u0022\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"cubinator","CreatedById":150330,"CreatedDateTime":"2016-10-01T19:38:34Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nSpectacular work! I love seeing others thinking outside the box as I have!\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"TheJangleMan","CreatedById":158481,"CreatedDateTime":"2016-10-03T11:17:28Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\namazing!!!\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"IronCretin","CreatedById":158162,"CreatedDateTime":"2016-10-10T20:10:07Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nWhat is this sorcery?\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Castille7","CreatedById":101668,"CreatedDateTime":"2016-10-31T19:07:46Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nMy brain hurts thinking about it!\u00A0\u003Cimg alt=\u0022:confused:\u0022 data-emoticon=\u0022\u0022 src=\u0022//kerbal-forum-uploads.s3.us-west-2.amazonaws.com/emoticons/default_k_huh.gif\u0022 title=\u0022:confused:\u0022\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\n"}]}